Ing metung a maleparan a kabaldugan ning '''kasangkapan''' (''tool'' king Ingles, ''instrumento'' o ''herramienta'' king Castila), metung a bageng gagamitan bang mamilatan kareng aduang sakup o panig (''domains'') a sasaup bang mika mas matalab kimut o dapat ning metung a panig ketang metung. Ing pekasimpling kasangkapan, ila pin deng [[:en:simple machine|simpling maquina]] (''simple machines''). Alimbawa, ing baluat (''crowbar'') gagana ya antimong ''lever''. Cuntoru midadayu ya king ''pivot point'', lalung darakal ing sikanan o fuerzang dadalan king ''lever''. Keraklan, martiliu ya ing atiu king pilatan ning gamat ning magobra ampo ing pakung buri nang turan.

Deng kasangkapan ing pekamaulagang bageng gagamitan da reng tau bang mukiat king babo ning [[:en:food chain|food chain]]; kapamilatan ning pamanimbentu kareng kasangkapan, agiu rong agagawa deng bageng e ra agiung daptan deng katawan da, alimbawa ing pamangamit king [[tandus]] o [[pana]] king pamakamate kareng darakpan dang animal, uling e la makanian katilus deng karelang ipan ba lang taglus kareng balat da reng animal.  

Ing telepono metung yang kasangkapan king comunicacion a mamilatan kareng aduang taung misasabi king metung a lebel. At king pilatan ning balang talagamit ampo ing suge ning comunicacion o ''communication network'' king aliwang lebel. King sakup ning tecnologiang media o comunicacion minuna rang akilala deng keraklan ing metung a e karaniwan aspetu ning kekatamung pamiugnayan o relacion kareng kekatamung kasangkapan. Sikat ya i Marshall McLuhan ketang sinabi nang "We shape our tools. And then our tools shape us." Ing amanuan na, ya pin itang maliliaring deng pamakiugnayan tamu kareng aliwang tau, makibage la king kekatamung pamangamit kareng bayung kasangkapan, at ing pamaniamasan tamu kareng kasangkapan a gagamitan ta na. 

Apatunayan ning pamagumasid a [[:Category:Tool-using species|dakal lang uring animal deng gagamit kasangkapan]], kayabe la reng matsin, miayaliwang uring ayup, [[:en:sea otter|sea otter]], at aliwa pa. Aniang mumuna, isipan da reng filosofo (''philosophers'') a den mung tau ing maki agiung ''gawang'' kasangkapan, anggang apagumasdan do reng zoologist deng ayap<ref>[http://users.ox.ac.uk/~kgroup/diameter_select.pdf Selection of tool diameter by New Caledonian crows ''Corvus moneduloides''], Jackie Chappell and Alex Kacelnik November 29, 2003</ref> ampo reng matsin<ref>[http://williamcalvin.com/bk2/bk2ch3.htm The Throwing Madonna: Essays on the Brain], William H. Calvin</ref><ref>[http://www.pbs.org/saf/1504/resources/transcript.htm Scientific American Frontiers, Program#1504 "Chimp Minds"] transcript PBS.org Airdate February 9, 2005</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollinghillswildlife.com/animals/c/chimpanzee/|title=Rolling Hills Wildlife Adventure: Chimpanzee}}</ref> a gagawang kasangkapan. Ngeni, ing alang kalupang kaugnayan da reng tau kareng kasangkapan ya pin itang deng tau mu kabud ing uri o species a gagamit kareng kasangkapan bang gawang ''aliwang'' kasangkapan.{{Citation needed|date=July 2007}}

Keraklan kareng [[:en:anthropology|anthropologist]] maniwala lang ing pamangamit kareng kasangkapan metung yang maulagang takbang king [[:en:human evolution|pamagbayu o evolucion ning meto ketawan]].<ref name=lilley>Sam Lilley, ''[http://books.google.com/books?id=Cj0EAAAAMAAJ&q=tools+history&dq=tools+history&pgis=1 Men, Machines and History: The Story of Tools and Machines in Relation to Social Progress]'', 1948 Cobbett Press.</ref> Mika [[opposable thumb]] ya ing tau — a magamitan king pamanalan kareng kasangkapan — at misnang miragdagan ing kayang kabiasnan, a sinaup king pamangamit kareng kasangkapan.<ref>[http://www.emc.maricopa.edu/faculty/farabee/biobk/BioBookHumEvol.html Primates and Their Adaptations, 2001], M.J. Farabee. Retrieved on November 6, 2006.</ref>
